com.mad.p03.np2020.routine.Home.ViewHolder

Class MyHomeViewHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder
      • com.mad.p03.np2020.routine.Home.ViewHolder.MyHomeViewHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.view.GestureDetector.OnGestureListener, android.view.View.OnTouchListener

    public class MyHomeViewHolder
extends androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder
implements android.view.View.OnTouchListener, android.view.GestureDetector.OnGestureListener
    To be used with the adapter HomePageAdapter. This holds reference to the id of the view resource. This is where we implement onTouchListener and onGestureListener to listen to swipes, clicks and drag.
    Since:
    04-06-2020
